sne-msft/ |publisher=InvestorPlace |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Bn2pyghH?url=http://investorplace.com/2012/02/will-smart-tvs-end-the-game-console-business-ntdoy-aapl-sne-msft/ |archive-date=2012-10-30 |accessdate=2012-02-24 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Guardian end">{{Cite web |date=2013-01-04 |title=PlayStation 2 manufacture ends after 12 years |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2013/jan/04/playstation-2-manufacture-ends-years?INTCMP=SRCH |publisher=[[衛報|The Guardian]] |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Df1TxpH3?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2013/jan/04/playstation-2-manufacture-ends-years?INTCMP=SRCH |archive-date=2013-01-14 |accessdate=2013-01-04 |dead-url=no}}</ref>由於這些裝置的成長速度極快，許多分析家認為第八世代可能是家用遊戲機的最後一個世代。<ref name="Guardian end" />在發售前就已透過群眾募款獲得數百萬美元資金的遊戲機[[OUYA|OUYA]]，將開源自由開發和免費遊玩的商業模式帶入了第八世代主機。<ref>http://www.pocketgamer.biz/r/PG.Biz/Astrogun+news/news.asp?c=43243</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=存档副本 |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/05/09/sony-microsoft-going-heavily-on-free-to-play-next-gen-says-e/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129063402/http://www.joystiq.com/2013/05/09/sony-microsoft-going-heavily-on-free-to-play-next-gen-says-e/ |archive-date=2014-11-29 |access-date=2014-12-28 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[GameStick|GameStick]]、[[NVIDIA_Shield|NVIDIA Shield]]、[[Ouya|Ouya]]和[[Steam#Steam_Box|Steam Box]]等公司都試著想加入市場競爭；但卻都很少被人以第八世代遊戲機來稱呼。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Langshaw |first=Mark |last2=Reynolds |first2=Matthew |date=2013-01-13 |title=Can Android consoles Ouya, Project Shield challenge PlayStation, Xbox? |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/news/a450282/can-android-consoles-ouya-project-shield-challenge-playstation-xbox.html |publisher=DigitalSpy.com |accessdate=2013-03-07}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Kelly |first=Tadhg |date=January 10, 2013 |title=With Ouya, GameStick, Steam Box and more, will 2013 be the year of the 'microconsole'? |url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/with-ouya-gamestick-steam-box-and-more-will-2013-be-the-year-of-the-microconsole/ |publisher=Edge Online |accessdate=2013-03-07}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Pereira |first=Chris |date=2013-01-15 |title=Digital and Nontraditional: Breaking Down Ouya, Steam Box, And Other New Wave Systems |url=http://www.1up.com/features/breaking-down-ouya-steam-box-new-wave-systems |publisher=1up.com |accessdate=2013-03-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130221190432/http://www.1up.com/features/breaking-down-ouya-steam-box-new-wave-systems |archivedate=2013-02-21}}</ref>但遊戲機的高低端分化益趨明顯，方便快速手機應用、獨立創作遊戲等，以及巨額投資的大作品、有職業比賽環境的網路遊戲等。本部分提到的主要是大製作的遊戲，可以提供完全的享受。或是高度的討論。

